1. *Napisao* je svoju prvu knjigu u 18. veku. (He wrote his first book in the 18th century.)
2. On je *napisao* mnogo knjiga. (He wrote many books.)
3. *Napisao* je naučne radove. (He wrote scientific papers.)
4. *Napisali* smo zajedničku knjigu. (We wrote a joint book.)
5. Oni su *napisali* zanimljive priče. (They wrote interesting stories.)
6. *Napisali* smo slovo zahvalnosti. (We wrote a letter of thanks.)
7. On je *napisao* novu knjigu. (He wrote a new book.)
8. *Napisali* su mnogo pesama. (They wrote many songs.)
9. Ona je *napisala* pismo. (She wrote a letter.)
10. *Napisali* smo pismo roditeljima. (We wrote a letter to our parents.)